## Latent

- The NAS snapshot of `memory_observations` may deserve a tiny restore
  script next to it, so "archived" stays honestly restorable.
- If auto-memory migration surfaces facts that contradict current Brain
  pages, that's curation work, not migration work — flag, don't guess.

## Out of scope

